<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>JESUS SHALL REIGN WHERE'ER THE SUN</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Khawi ale nisuoh na chengah,
 Isu Lal in vaihawm ina;
 Tha det a haih masang sieh in,
 A Lalgam lien deuh deuh ina.

[V2]
 2. Gamtin, mitin pau chuom chuom te,
 A hehpih a cheng la sau;
 Naupanghaw Aw chun phuong ina,
 Deihsak tungna A Min pien au.

[V3]
 3. A kawma paucham tawplo a,
 Pahchak tawplo a chawihat ding;
 Zingkal tin ngetna ah A min,
 Gimlim banga zam to zing ding.

[V4]
 4. Leichunga mitin hung tho in,
 Lalpen chuh chawihatna pie'n au;
 Angel lasa'n hungkum kitin,
 Leiin gensawn hen la, Amen.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>153</hymn_number>
</song>